---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Family Friendly UK"
  description="Family Friendly UK was started by Natalie, a mum on a mission to find genuinely family-friendly restaurants across the UK. Here's the story behind the site."
>
  <article class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-hero">
        <div class="leaf" aria-hidden="true">🌿</div>
        <h1>Built by a parent, for parents.</h1>
        <p class="kicker">The story behind Family Friendly UK</p>
      </header>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>How this all started</h2>
        <p>
          Family Friendly UK was started by Natalie, a mum to a wonderful little girl. The idea
          came from a problem she kept running into — whether visiting a new part of the
          country or exploring closer to home, the same question always came up: <em>where can
          we actually eat out as a family?</em> Not just somewhere that tolerates children, but
          somewhere that genuinely welcomes them. Somewhere with highchairs, a decent kids
          menu, space for a buggy, and food worth travelling for.
        </p>
        <p>
          After searching for a resource that didn't exist, Natalie decided to build it
          herself. Family Friendly UK is the guide she always wished she'd had — honest,
          practical, and built around the things that actually matter when you're dining out
          with little ones.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section about-section--soft">
        <h2>The Screen-Free Restaurant Pack</h2>
        <p>
          Natalie is also an artist, which is why alongside the directory she has created the
          <strong>Screen-Free Restaurant Pack</strong> — a free downloadable activity pack designed
          to encourage children to draw, imagine, and be creative while they wait for their food.
          No screens, just pencils and imagination.
        </p>
        <a href="/downloads" class="btn-download">
          Download the free pack →
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Drawing futures we love</h2>
        <p>
          We also partner with <strong>Future We Love</strong>, an art and creativity platform
          built around a simple idea: when people open their hearts and imagine better futures,
          those futures become more possible. Every month we feature children's artwork
          submitted through our free creative downloads — drawings of futures kids would love
          to see. It's one of our favourite things.
        </p>
        <a href="https://futurewelove.com" class="link-explore" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Explore Future We Love →
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="about-cta">
        <h2>Always free for families.</h2>
        <p>
          Family Friendly UK is always free for families. If you know a great
          family-friendly restaurant we've missed, we'd love to hear about it.
        </p>
        <a href="/suggest" class="btn btn-terracotta btn-lg">Suggest a restaurant →</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about {
  background: var(--cream);
  padding: 64px 0 88px;
}
.about-hero {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 64px;
  max-width: 720px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
.about-hero .leaf {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  display: inline-block;
  transform: rotate(-12deg);
}
.about-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
  color: var(--green);
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.about-hero .kicker {
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-style: italic;
}
.about-section {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 40px 44px;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto 32px;
  position: relative;
}
.about-section--soft {
  background: var(--green-pale);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,80,22,0.06);
}
.about-section h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.625rem;
  color: var(--green);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.about-section p {
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.about-section p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }
.about-section em { color: var(--terracotta); font-style: italic; }
.about-section strong { color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; }
.btn-download {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 22px;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  background: var(--green);
  color: white;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
}
.btn-download:hover { background: var(--green-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
.link-explore {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 14px;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  font-weight: 500;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid currentColor;
  padding-bottom: 1px;
  transition: color 0.15s;
}
.link-explore:hover { color: var(--terracotta-light); }
.about-cta {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 64px;
  max-width: 640px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  padding: 0 16px;
}
.about-cta h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  color: var(--green);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.about-cta p {
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .about-section { padding: 32px 24px; }
}
</style>
